    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Romanus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>dom</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Antioc</abbr><ex>hia</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>sib</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> et Ateriae <lb n="6"/>Sabinae <expan><abbr>coni</abbr><ex>ugi</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LX et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Aurelio <lb n="8"/>Romaniano filio </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et Aureli<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>e Va<supplied reason="lost">leri</supplied>a<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>coniug</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld von tordierten Halbsäulen eingefasst; oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Fries mit Hunden, die einen Hasen jagen; darüber Giebel mit Gorgoneieon; über den Giebelschrägen Meerwesen. Z. 9: auf der Leiste unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes; Buchstaben zur Zeit der Edition von CIL 03, 04182 noch komplett lesbar. (B): Balla - Buocz - Kádár - Mócsy - Szentléleky: Z. 8: fil[i]o; CIL 03, 10920: Z. 9: Au[reliae Valeriae coniug.]; Tóth: Z. 9: Aureliae Valeriae c[o]niug(i).</p>
            </div>
